All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
Bullet
Bullet class to create the sprite of a bullet being fired by Pacman.
DatabaseManager
This class manages the PostgreSQL database connection and provides methods for interacting with the database.
Diagonal_Ghost
Diagonal Ghost class that creates a ghost enemy that bounces around the screen.
Left_Ghost
Left Ghost class that creates the ghost enemy that moves from right to left.
Main
The Main class to launch the Pacman Shooter Java Application
Pacman
Pacman class to keep track of the player character.
PacmanWindow
The PacmanWindow class initializes the window in which the Pacman Shooter application will be played in.
Sprite
Sprite class to inherit all the attributes of a sprite on the screen.
StartMenu
The StartMenu class creates the panel in which all elements of the Pacman shooter would be inserted into.
